data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!  Move in ready pool home in The Meadows of Countryway in Tampa, Florida. This spacious three-bedroom, two-bathroom home, offers a living room, dining room and family room with high ceilings for great entertaining. The kitchen has custom cabinetry with sleek granite countertops  complete with new stainless steel GE appliances.  The two updated bathrooms boast contemporary fixtures and finishes. The bedrooms have a split plan with the master suite offering a spacious private retreat with access to the pool.  No expense has been spared at this home.  Special Features:  New driveway pavers (2023), new screens in the lanai (2020), new washer dryer (2021), new HVAC (2021), new roof (2019), new garage door (2022) and exterior painted (2023).  There is nothing for you to do, but move in.  Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, Tampa International Airport, Hospitals, doctors' offices, beaches and many attractions. Assumable mortgage available. This is the perfect time to make this turnkey home your own slice of Florida paradise.
